<p>Zero plus subscribers can save multiple custom fasts as presets for easier switching.</p>

<h1 id="history">History</h1>
<p>The history screen displays all your fasting statistics. The tabs at the top enable you to switch between the statistics and calendar view. Tapping on each day in the calendar view displays the fasting statistics for that day.</p>

