  <li>Fasting Zones. These are Anabolic, Catabolic, Fat Burning, Ketosis and Deep Ketosis. While you can see the current fasting zone youâ€™re in, with Zero Plus youâ€™ll be able to get detailed info on each fasting zone.</li>
  <li>Saving a custom fast as a Preset.</li>
  <li>Additional statistics in the History tab. These are:
    <ul>
      <li>Time in Fasting Zones</li>
